## Notes
- Currently using CSV files for data storage
- Barcode API: `https://barcodeapi.org/api/code128/{barcode}`
- Labels generated at 300 DPI
- Font: `monofonto rg.otf`
- Network access currently disabled
- All static files in `/static/` directory
